Vril: the Power of the Coming Race, Paperback by Lytton, Edward Bulwer Lytton, Baron, ISBN 1448636922, ISBN-13 9781448636921, Like New Used, Free shipping in the US

A legendary book, which was the starting point for the genre of science fiction, Theosophy, the New Age, The Force, and modern day conspiracy theories. It's tale of a subterranean Master Race, able to control a mysterious energy force, called the Vril. It inspired the Vril Society in Germany and beyond, and was believe by many to be very thinly disguised owe it to yourself to peruse this highly entertaining and engaging seminal work, and see where many of our widely held beliefs today were spawned!
